misc: Has a habit of getting lost on golf course grounds
Does not spit in the glass
biography: Janne, a familiar face at the Hector Trophée, is known for his generous spirit and unwavering commitment to the sport. A proud member of Revontuli Golf, Janne's presence is always appreciated, even if he occasionally finds himself taking the scenic route between holes.

With seven past appearances at the Hector Trophée, Janne is hoping that Hector Trophée 2025 will be his lucky year. While the coveted Hector Trophée and the Victor Trophy have eluded him thus far, Janne's dedication and sportsmanship make him a respected competitor.

Off the course, Janne is known for his impeccable manners and refusal to engage in uncouth behavior, such as spitting in the glass. His fellow golfers appreciate his gentlemanly conduct and camaraderie.
